Package energy.usef.agr.workflow.plan.connection.profile

Workflow classes for connection profiles in the plan phase of the Aggregator.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AgrCreateConnectionProfileCoordinator
    Coordinator class in charge of the workflow populating the Profile power values of the connection portfolio.
    AgrCreateUdiCoordinator
    Coordinator class in charge of the workflow populating the Profile power values of the connection portfolio.
    AgrUpdateElementDataStoreCoordinator
    Coordinator class in charge of the workflow updating the element data store.
    AgrUpdateElementDataStoreEvent
    Event to trigger the workflow to update the element data store.
    AgrUpdateElementDataStoreParameter
    This class contains the enumerations of possible parameters for the workflow to update the element data store.
    CreateConnectionProfileEvent
    Event to trigger the workflow populating the Porfile power values for the connection portfolio.
    CreateConnectionProfileStepParameter
    This class contains the enumerations of possible parameters for the workflow population the Profile power values in the connecion portfolio.
    CreateUdiEvent
    Event to trigger the workflow populating the Udis for the connection portfolio.
    CreateUdiStepParameter
    This class contains the enumerations of possible parameters for the workflow population the Profile power values in the connection portfolio.

    Input parameters.

    CreateUdiStepParameter.IN
    Input parameters:
    PERIOD: LocalDate
    PTU_DURATION: Integer Duration in minutes.
    CONNECTION_PORTFOLIO_DTO_LIST: List of ConnectionPortfolioDto's.

    CreateUdiStepParameter.OUT
    Output parameters:
    CONNECTION_PORTFOLIO_DTO_LIST: List of ConnectionPortfolioDto's.
    UDI_EVENTS_PER_UDI_MAP: Map of String (udi endpoint) to a List of UdiEventDto's.
